  <description><![CDATA[<p>Kimberley Alpine Resort is located right at the foot of the slopes and offers ski in/ski out accommodation and a variety of skiing terrain in a beautiful setting with stunning views of the <em>Rockie</em>s.</p>
<p>The runs are well groomed and lift queues are rare, making it a great choice for families and beginners. Kimberley's downtown centre with its selection of shops, bars and restaurants has a Bavarian theme and is a short 5 minute bus ride from Kimberley Alpine resort.</p>]]></description>
